fields.Description:
Set on a wide block with excellent frontage on the high side of a sought-after street, this charming double-brick home boasts soaring high ceilings, federation details, and a desirable north-rear aspect.

Enveloped by cottage-style gardens with picturesque surrounds, this property is ideally positioned to enjoy a peaceful lifestyle, whilst being within walking distance to school, parks, and buses. 

Ready to move in and with enormous potential, this is a rare opportunity to capture the ideal location for your dream family home.


- On approx. 800.9sqm wide block on tranquil and highly sought-after street
- Reliable double brick home with three spacious bedrooms and built-ins
- Original timber floorboards, high ceilings, and ducted air conditioning
- Gas kitchen with ample storage opening to alfresco dining courtyard 
- Third bedroom acts as second living with direct patio and garden access
- Bathroom features separate tub, additional powder room behind garage
- Extended single car lock-up garage plus extra off-street parking space
- Convenient external laundry off garage and stunning cottage style garden
- Seven-minute walk to zoned Gordon East school, four minutes to buses
- Only two minutes to Gordon shops and trains, steps to stunning parks
